{"tid":1013113,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇消極論","createTime":"2019-02-08T06:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T00:04:03.000Z","uid":125976,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"22dacbfadc012628376dabf0bafd44a570ffe600","tid":1013113,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"生存係苦，所以唔生下一代，唔想製造痛苦，亦唔想為資本家提供奴隸用<br />\n<br />\n消費最後獲利最大嘅都係毫無生產力嘅資本家，所以盡量減少消費<br />\n<br />\n全球大印銀紙，平民賺錢都不敵通脹，所以將銀紙轉晒做黃金 / 公用股<br />\n<br />\n買樓又助長香港四大家族嘅淫威，都係搵份最低工資嘅工排公屋<br />\n<br />\n人生靠首抽，抽到爛牌點玩都係輸家，都係屈屈就就過埋下半生佢算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549e455f178d802c10331d0228400e3f1f0f7d78","tid":1013113,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪太渴望有所成就所以先抑鬱?"},{"pid":"e9b952a1bfa2fd6c14ea5423a4139e298e44f105","tid":1013113,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"549e455f178d802c10331d0228400e3f1f0f7d78","tid":1013113,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪太渴望有所成就所以先抑鬱?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"唔關事，好細個已經抑鬱，當然期望現實落差都會加重抑鬱"},{"pid":"8c86860089d654ae975b8f99058b491bb254802e","tid":1013113,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:26:11.000Z","msg":"咁可以點，往後幾十年你諗住點過，有咩目標<br />\n難道你提早。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379fc4f27e37230057275805af40bc817a7f667d","tid":1013113,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9b952a1bfa2fd6c14ea5423a4139e298e44f105","tid":1013113,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"549e455f178d802c10331d0228400e3f1f0f7d78","tid":1013113,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪太渴望有所成就所以先抑鬱?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"唔關事，好細個已經抑鬱，當然期望現實落差都會加重抑鬱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪錯覺，我覺得你對外界有種恐懼、惶恐、焦慮，不如試下放開啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:墮落"},{"pid":"c876c785d4f95400e97776eb0d7d0fc668708a46","tid":1013113,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"有時，接受不完美、限制同錯誤，會好過啲<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己都憧憬得太多"},{"pid":"8c5b9171036cbd1dba840bc2fd2398351ea70ece","tid":1013113,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"太攰"},{"pid":"9e2915626b7cfe9d77c61d82ad534e5a30fb7e0d","tid":1013113,"uid":39921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"做完乜乜，最後得益都係乜乜<br />\n但你之所以會做乜乜，唔係因為對你有利益先做架咩？因為最後大商家會得益，所以連自己利益都要放棄?"},{"pid":"bff2d1e9140520f18b17912812703a0ffec98114","tid":1013113,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"早幾日睇到新聞講林村又斷樹，覺得<br />\n<br />\n人就好似一棵許願樹一樣，拋擲太多願望上去，承受太多就會倒塌"},{"pid":"142dccf57172343a6b897e9bd6cb9911121a81f8","tid":1013113,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:52:27.000Z","msg":"幾諷刺，笑"},{"pid":"8dcf0632577e6f599e6430d0d3b9aced65f4327b","tid":1013113,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e2915626b7cfe9d77c61d82ad534e5a30fb7e0d","tid":1013113,"uid":39921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"做完乜乜，最後得益都係乜乜<br />\n但你之所以會做乜乜，唔係因為對你有利益先做架咩？因為最後大商家會得益，所以連自己利益都要放棄?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"由佢繼續攬住套消極論過埋嗰幾十年啦，咁樣最輕鬆乜都唔洗諗，唔洗花氣力改變<br />\n<br />\n唔好成日寸人乜你咁on9做埋啲無意義嘅嘢，助長仆街政權、大商家。其實呢種論點可以無限延伸至任何行為<br />\n<br />\n佢依家繼續生存嘅最大目的可能係盡力傳播佢套消極論比最多嘅人before佢拜拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7bd17b0506320181cc87c5d180be7e63f4c89c","tid":1013113,"uid":105511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"生存方面我覺得窮人就唔好生仔 最好拖都唔好拍 窮人生仔冇幸福 見過太多失敗例子 唔知為咩<br />\n同埋生仔好處=零 生仔唔會改善到你生活 只會加重你負擔 最後仲會俾個仔叫做廢老<br />\n拍拖結婚都係衰野 話分就分 話離婚就離婚 付出既就冇晒 仲要倒貼 所以自己一個反而最好 <br />\n消費可以改善生活質素 所以商家同買家既關係=互惠互利 商家得到錢 你提高左生活質素 <br />\n你想要幾多就俾幾多錢 均真過生仔拍拖好多 明買明賣"},{"pid":"8e9a5d278a2d9f919b59e6f327890054668aab2f","tid":1013113,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿左向寫右由得記，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓"},{"pid":"0e55dd834aa51e2397a328b4a7272fd6b9d54345","tid":1013113,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e9a5d278a2d9f919b59e6f327890054668aab2f","tid":1013113,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿左向寫右由得記，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f170a6f214d67bef13bb43ec5cc526295ce5fd","tid":1013113,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67945cf5c83d9f0cf7b68d153b19bed47ac5270c","tid":1013113,"uid":31733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"上年成日番d夜更part，<br />\n一到深夜就開始諗負面野，<br />\n而家辭左無番，<br />\n但都有時突然覺得好down<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9eb1b8e611852c35cf7471ca85c42e25614a8d6","tid":1013113,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:56:26.000Z","msg":"是但la"},{"pid":"a46073e41119cb3a3776724535f6b244d85892c3","tid":1013113,"uid":169133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bff2d1e9140520f18b17912812703a0ffec98114","tid":1013113,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"早